  "lastUpdatedOn": "2012-08-17",
  "religion": "Cher is a Buddhist, though she admits to not practicing as much as she would like.",
  "politicalViews": "Cher is a longtime supporter of the Democratic Party and a spokesperson, supporter, and icon for the gay community.",
  "author": "Tom Kershaw",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "Cher, whose real name is Cheryl Sarkisian, was born in El Centro, California and raised there and in Fresno, California."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "Cher had a tumultuous childhood, where religion was probably not present–at least in any significant amount. New, she calls herself a Buddhist, though a self-proclaimed lazy one. She once admitted:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "http://buddhistcelebrities.blogspot.com/2010/12/cher-lazy-buddhist.html",
      "sourceTitle": "Cher, A Lazy Buddhist",
      "text": "I am the worst Buddhist ever. I love reading it and saying the prayers, but I'm such a lazy-assed Buddhist. I meditate but only when I want to. I'm so stubborn. I don't like to be forced to do anything. If you try and force me, it's the wrong thing to do."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "But even though she doesn't give it her all–and is willing to admit it–Buddhism is the right religion for Cher. She says:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.tricycle.com/p/1881",
      "sourceTitle": "Who's Buddhist Now? Cher! ",
      "text": "I've played around with Buddhism for years. As corny as it sounds, the soul of the universe, everything that I need, I can find in its practice."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.cherworld.com/cher-news/inside-chers-hollywood-apartment/",
      "sourceTitle": "Inside Cher's Hollywood Apartment",
      "text": "It's possible that it's all an act and she really just likes Buddhist art. An expose of her Los Angeles apartment revealed 4,000 spare feet of Asian sculptures, furniture, and decor."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "text": "Do you believe in… politics"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.newsmeat.com/celebrity_political_donations/Cher.php",
      "sourceTitle": "Cher's Federal Campaign Contribution Report",
      "text": "Cher is a longtime and active Democrat. She's donated $11,400 to the Democratic Party and left-leaning interest groups since 1988, when she threw her support behind Michael Dukakis."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R5lGYw6hx_A",
      "sourceTitle": "Cher Talks About Hillary Clinton and Barack Obama",
      "text": "More recently, Cher bucked Barack Obama in favor of Hillary Clinton in the 2008 Democratic primaries,"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.politico.com/politico44/2012/06/julia-roberts-cher-fundraise-with-obama-125515.html",
      "sourceTitle": "Julia Roberts, Cher fundraise with Obama",
      "text": "but when Obama got the nomination, she endorsed him and did so again during his 2012 re-election bid."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "But it's not just that Cher supports the Democrats, she's been a loud critic of conservative Republicans, particularly during the Bush administration. She once said, both condemning George W. Bush and addressing those who criticize celebrities for expressing their views:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.lyricsfreak.com/c/cher/biography.html",
      "sourceTitle": "Cher – Biography",
      "text": "You know, I think it's the duty of artists to say what they want, in favor or in opposition. Unfortunately, I think that… because of 9/11, if you say anything opposed to the [Bush] administration, somehow they've been able to wrap themselves in the flag, so that if you have any opposing viewpoint, you're unpatriotic."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "And when Mitt Romney won the Republican nomination for president, Cher hilariously tweeted:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.thegatewaypundit.com/2012/05/its-time-for-obama-to-apologize-for-chers-awful-tweets/cher-nuts/",
      "sourceTitle": "Cher Nuts",
      "text": "If ROMNEY gets elected I don't know if I can breathe same air as Him & His Right Wing Racist Homophobic Women Hating Tea Bagger Masters."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "Awesome."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://thenewgay.net/2011/03/what-makes-a-gay-icon.html",
      "sourceTitle": "What Makes a Gay Icon?",
      "text": "Cher is quite invested in the gay community as well. Not only is she an absolute goddess, having won numerous awards and accolades from LGBT organizations,"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://gossiponthis.com/2011/05/10/chaz-bono-cher-daughter-son-talks-sex-change-oprah/",
      "sourceTitle": "Chaz Bono – Cher's Daughter Who Turned Into Her Son – Talks Sex Change On Oprah",
      "text": "her daughter (now her son) is a transgender man,"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "who has forced Cher to truly examine her feelings on homosexuality and caused her to become one of the gay community's most outspoken advocates for equality and fair treatment."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "In short, Cher's about as liberal a Democrat as they come."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    }
  ],
